but i am not relinquishing my office,'' riera said in a telephone interview. ``i do not recognize the authority of noriega. i recognize the authority of president (eric arturo) delvalle,'' whose feb. 26 ouster was engineered by the military strongman
riera said ms. moron is a noriega ally and had a hand in a ``break-in'' of his office wednesday while he was in strasbourg, france, to lobby for a european parliament resolution condemning noriega
