similar disputes among panamanian diplomats divided over the noriega-delvalle imbroglio have occurred in other foreign capitals including in london, washington and mexico city
the united states, where a federal jury last month indicted noriega on drug trafficking and money laundering charges, recognizes delvalle
the belgian government had no immediate reaction to the change of command at the panamanian embassy
