officials at the office of sen. edward m. kennedy, d-mass., said the senator's niece _ victoria lawford pender, 30, the daughter of pat kennedy lawford and the late actor peter lawford _ gave birth to an eight-pound, nine-ounce girl at 6:30 a.m. at georgetown university hospital
the infant, named alexandra lawford pender, was due on the day of the super tuesday presidential primary elections but arrived a few days late
